{
  "stem": "888.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was in, sort of in the springtime, so it wasn't really that hot or anything like that, that it wasn't-- it was very uncomfortable.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And as far as sleeping, I don't recall.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I mean, I suppose we must've fallen asleep curled up or some-- you know, it was--",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, there wasn't room.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, a railroad car is only maybe from the wall to the sofa, and probably this length of the living room.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's about it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I figure there must've been about 50 people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At least 50 people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, I mean, children, you know, and-- there were a lot of people were huddled, you know, mainly towards the walls of the place, and--",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As I could recall, probably it must've taken about between five to six days, something like that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, there was places that they stopped, you know, and then--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember they should-- that they give us, gave us any, any food whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think water.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Water.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't-- you know, I suppose whatever they took along.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Bread, you know, like in Hungary they made these big breads, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So it must've been a couple of breads, and maybe whatever else I don't recall, you know?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not very well, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I mean, there was families that I knew.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But don't forget that there was also not necessarily people from Satmar itself, you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because Satmar people, I knew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I would say, at least 60%, 70% I knew.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they brought in-- from all the surrounding areas, they brought in people which we didn't know, you know?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they brought them into the same ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, of course, you know, so then we arrived in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
